{"id":273500,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/【图看天朝】民众现场声援南周第二日/","date":"2013-01-08T09:26:38Z","modified":"2013-09-07T21:12:30Z","title":"【图说天朝】民众现场声援南周第二日","content":"<p>8日下午，民众现场声援南周的第二天，仍有不少民众陆续出现在南方周末广州总部大门口以献花、举横幅等方式进行声援。值得一提的是，今日下午，有数名反对南方周末的毛派人士出现，与声援南方周末的人群形成对峙。除此之外，有不少大陆网友乃至港澳的网友以上传手持标语照片的方式挺南周。</p>\n<p>注：据网友反映，昨日起多名献花的民众遭到警方骚扰，一些微博大V、推友被喝茶。</p>\n\n\t\t<style type='text/css'>\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 {\n\t\t\t\tmargin: auto;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-item {\n\t\t\t\tfloat: left;\n\t\t\t\tmargin-top: 10px;\n\t\t\t\ttext-align: center;\n\t\t\t\twidth: 25%;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 img {\n\t\t\t\tborder: 2px solid #cfcfcf;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t#gallery-1 .gallery-caption {\n\t\t\t\tmargin-left: 0;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t/* see gallery_shortcode() in wp-includes/media.php */\n\t\t</style>\n\t\t<div id='gallery-1' class='gallery galleryid-273500 gallery-columns-4 gallery-size-thumbnail'><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/qcGPX.jpg'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/qcGPX-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-273520\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/qcGPX-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/qcGPX-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt>\n\t\t\t\t<dd class='wp-caption-text gallery-caption' id='gallery-1-273520'>\n\t\t\t\t8日上午 南周大门口被安装监控\n\t\t\t\t</dd></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/BAEawCdCcAEUSvx.jpg'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/BAEawCdCcAEUSvx-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-273513\" srcset=\"h